    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in truly mint condition, representing a rare find for the discerning buyer. Every aspect of the car has been meticulously maintained, from the flawless original paint to the pristine, showroom-quality interior. Mechanically, it is perfect, with the engine and transmission operating as smoothly as the day it was manufactured. There are no signs of wear, leaks, or cosmetic imperfections anywhere on the vehicle. This is a collector-grade example that drives beautifully and requires absolutely nothing but a new owner who appreciates perfection.",
